"\n"
"Prekreslí obrazovku a znovu načíta obrázky, ktoré sa zmenili.\n"
"\n"

#. [topic]: id=general_commands
#: data/core/help.cfg:810
msgid ""
"\n"
"Bring up theme selection menu.\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""
"\n"
"Zobrazí menu výberu témy.\n"
"\n"

#. [topic]: id=general_commands
